      public Seat getSeatByNumber(int seatNumber, SeatType seatType)
      Searches for seat object.

      Using the provided seatNumber and seatType, this method returns an instance of the desired object on completion and returns null on failure

      Parameters:
      seatNumber - Interger attached to the Seat object for identification
      seatType - An enum attached to different levels of membership seating
      Returns:
      Instance of a Seat object with the given seatNumber and seatType
